#: ../../docs/training_manual/create_vector_data/actions.rst:12
msgid "**The goal for this lesson:** To learn how to add custom actions."
msgstr "Cíl této lekce. Naučit se jak přidat běznou akci."

#: ../../docs/training_manual/create_vector_data/actions.rst:28
msgid "Open the :guilabel:`Layer Properties` dialog."
msgstr "Otevřít: guilabel: dialog `Vlastnosti vrstvy` ."

#: ../../docs/training_manual/create_vector_data/actions.rst:29
msgid "Click on the :guilabel:`Fields` tab."
msgstr "Klikni na: guilabel:  kartu `Pole`."

#: ../../docs/training_manual/create_vector_data/actions.rst:30
msgid "Toggle editing mode:"
msgstr "Přepnout režim editace."

#: ../../docs/training_manual/create_vector_data/actions.rst:35
msgid "Add a new column:"
msgstr "Přidat nový sloupec:"

#: ../../docs/training_manual/create_vector_data/actions.rst:40
msgid "Enter the values below:"
msgstr "Vložit hodnoty níže:"

#: ../../docs/training_manual/create_vector_data/actions.rst:346
msgid "identify"
msgstr "identify"

#: ../../docs/training_manual/create_vector_data/actions.rst:62
msgid ""
"Click on the browse button (the :guilabel:`...` next to the "
":guilabel:`image` field)."
msgstr ""
"Kliknout na tlačítko procházet ( guilabel:`...` vedle :guilabel: pole "
"`obrázek` )."

#: ../../docs/training_manual/create_vector_data/actions.rst:67
msgid "Click :guilabel:`OK`."
msgstr "Kliknout :guilabel:`OK`."

#: ../../docs/training_manual/create_vector_data/actions.rst:68
msgid ""
"Associate all of the images with the correct features using this method."
msgstr ""
"Pro spojení všechech obrázků se správnými funkcemi použít tuto metodu."

#: ../../docs/training_manual/create_vector_data/actions.rst:70
msgid "Save your edits and exit edit mode."
msgstr "Ulož tvoje úpravy a opusť režim úprav."

#: ../../docs/training_manual/create_vector_data/actions.rst:348
msgid "symbologyAdd"
msgstr "symbologyAdd"

#: ../../docs/training_manual/create_vector_data/actions.rst:88
#: ../../docs/training_manual/create_vector_data/actions.rst:174
msgid ""
"What to do next varies according to your operating system, so choose the "
"appropriate course to follow:"
msgstr ""
"o dělat dál, se liší v závislosti na operačním systému, takže vyber vhodný "
"kurz a následuj:"

#: ../../docs/training_manual/create_vector_data/actions.rst:91
#: ../../docs/training_manual/create_vector_data/actions.rst:177
msgid "Windows"
msgstr "Okna"

#: ../../docs/training_manual/create_vector_data/actions.rst:93
msgid "Click on the :guilabel:`Type` dropdown and choose :guilabel:`Open`."
msgstr "Kliknout na :guilabel: rozbal `Typ`  a vyber  :guilabel:`otevřít`."

#: ../../docs/training_manual/create_vector_data/actions.rst:96
#: ../../docs/training_manual/create_vector_data/actions.rst:183
msgid "Ubuntu Linux"
msgstr "Ubuntu Linux"

#: ../../docs/training_manual/create_vector_data/actions.rst:105
msgid "Click on the :guilabel:`Type` dropdown and choose :guilabel:`Mac`."
msgstr "Klikni na :guilabel:`Typ` rozbal ho a vyber :guilabel:`Mac`."

#: ../../docs/training_manual/create_vector_data/actions.rst:113
msgid ""
"You want to open the image, and QGIS knows where the image is. All it needs "
"to do is to tell the :guilabel:`Action` where the image is."
msgstr ""
"Chceš otevřít obrázek, a QGIS  ví, kde obrázek je. Vše co potřebuješ je "
"napsat :guilabel:`Akce` tam kde je obrázek."

#: ../../docs/training_manual/create_vector_data/actions.rst:117
msgid "Select :guilabel:`image` from the list:"
msgstr "Vyber :guilabel:`obrázek` z nabídky: "

#: ../../docs/training_manual/create_vector_data/actions.rst:344
msgid "actionRun"
msgstr "actionRun"

#: ../../docs/training_manual/create_vector_data/actions.rst:143
msgid "Click the button itself to activate the tool."
msgstr "Klikni na toto tlačítko a aktivuj nástroj."

#: ../../docs/training_manual/create_vector_data/actions.rst:144
msgid "Using this tool, click on any of the three school properties."
msgstr ""
"Použití tohoto nástroje, kliknutím na kteroukoli z tří školních vlastností. "

#: ../../docs/training_manual/create_vector_data/actions.rst:350
msgid "symbologyRemove"
msgstr "symbologyRemove"

#: ../../docs/training_manual/create_vector_data/actions.rst:331
msgid "What's Next?"
msgstr "Kam dál?"
